TIER 2 — COVENANT NETWORK
Access to the Enhanced Covenant Framework is granted exclusively to ventures
that meet ALL of the following conditions:

1. The venture is formally onboarded into the Covenant Network by the
   Covenant Foundation.
2. The venture has executed a Revenue Share Agreement with the Covenant
   Foundation, committing 10% of gross revenue to the Foundation.
3. The venture uses the framework as a core part of its product or service.

Tier 2 access may be revoked by the Covenant Foundation if revenue share
obligations are not met.

